title: Ep: 003 - Architect Russ Tyson // Understanding a Client's Vision
description: In our third episode of Architecture, Design, & Photography we sit down with Russ Tyson, Principal at Whitten Architects. We discuss some recent projects we have collaborated on, sketching, and the process of understanding a client's vision.
author: info@trentbell.com (Trent Bell)
